 25 /*global gui, NodeFilter*/
 26 
 27 /**
 28  * @constructor
 29  * @implements NodeFilter
 30  * @param {!Array.<!string>} excludedNamespaces
 31  */
 32 gui.BlacklistNamespaceNodeFilter = function (excludedNamespaces) {
 33     "use strict";
 34     var /**@type{!Object.<!string, !boolean>}*/
 35         excludedNamespacesObj = {},
 36         FILTER_REJECT = NodeFilter.FILTER_REJECT,
 37         FILTER_ACCEPT = NodeFilter.FILTER_ACCEPT;
 38 
 39     /**
 40      * @param {?Node} node
 41      * @return {!number}
 42      */
 43     this.acceptNode = function (node) {
 44         if (!node || excludedNamespacesObj.hasOwnProperty(node.namespaceURI)) {
 45             return FILTER_REJECT;
 46         }
 47         return FILTER_ACCEPT;
 48     };
 49 
 50     function init() {
 51         excludedNamespaces.forEach(function(ns) {
 52             excludedNamespacesObj[ns] = true;
 53         });
 54     }
 55     init();
 56 };
